values:
When will I get to love again?

It's been almost a year since I met him... kind of like a dream in some faraway place. I don't want that again though. I don't want to see him, ever again. 

I need something real. I need to feel happy with someone again. Why can't I have that?

This shit is smokin.
But why's it gotta be so damn... fat? Think the dimension given for the width was like 0.91 inches. I would totally sell my Razr if this baby was sleeker and slimmer.

Here's a story for the posterity. 

One day, I decided that it was a good idea to take a caffeine pill 2 hours before my derivatives exam. The packet said it was equivalent to one cup of coffee. 200 mg of caffeine is more like 2.5 Red Bulls! Combined with the coke I drank earlier, that's 3 Red Bulls. Thus worst idea ever. 

I couldn't stop twitching for the next 3 hours. An hour into the exam, I was pretty sure I was doomed for that class. Considered the ramifications of withdrawing or dropping. But apparently the caffeine left my system, I calmed down, and I finished without appearing like an utter dumbass on paper, at least.

I makes the smarts decisions!
